PSX Buttons - Mac & Windows TrueType.

I made this font for a booklet I was preparing concerning Tekken 3ˆ. I needed the
PSX button characters so I made this font to help me include the Tekkenˆ characters
fight combination sequences etc.

The characters are as follows:-
1 - Right arrow
2 - Left arrow
3 - Up arrow
4 - Down arrow
5 - Diagonal Up Right arrow
6 - Diagonal Down Right arrow
7 - Diagonal Up Left arrow
8 - Diagonal Down Left arrow
Shift 1-8 are outline versions of the above arrows.

Where (eg. a/A) denotes Chars are the same Upper & Lowercase.

a/A - START
b/B - SELECT
c/C - Circle Button
l - L1 Button
L - L2 Button
r - R1 Button
R - R2 Button
s/S - Square Button
t/T - Triangle Button
x/X - X Button

Punctuation chars included are . , ( ) - + < > /

